## Limitations

This report is based on a limited selection of sources and may not capture all perspectives on the issue. The rapidly evolving nature of digital currencies means that new research and data could alter the current understanding of CBDCs. Additionally, the specific economic and regulatory contexts of different countries may lead to varied outcomes from the implementation of CBDCs, which this report does not fully explore.

